{"type": "article", "id": 20364, "title": "茶叶品牌包装", "description": "", "date": "2016-01-07T07:36:41Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 41, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607104207rbxvyDzhtAUcuTqJ.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t波兰的包装设计公司 Dmowski &amp; Co.要求为一家新成立的茶叶品牌 Blanca 设计包装，他们遵循了“少即是多”（less is more）的原则。logo 是一个大写的 B，画在手绘植物图案和深蓝色的背景上。宣传卡片和铝盒子上的标签都是白色的，上面简单地画了彩色的植物的图案，显得简单干净，文字选用了很小的字体，印在了植物上有特别的文艺气息。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104205adQSANgjzLcKGJ6r.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66574074\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071042057I9Sj2yVaARiOUTg.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66574074\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104206czXp5gKZCIbS8dMx.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66574074\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104206dA2xH0QiuD6RozMO.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.666\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}